Stores the system modules:

- The module file name MUST be Module.php
- The module namespace MUST be the same in all module files
- If you want to create sub namespaces its ok
- The module MUST have the folowing FOLDERS structure:

<module name> : All module files
  |_class	: Classes
  |_css		: CSS files
  |_doc		: The documenta
  |_img		: All module images
  |_js		: The javascript files 
  |_lang	: The language files
  |_template: Stores the templates
  
 For an example of module see /modules/example folder. 